#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autostart Manager"
msgstr "Menadžer samopokretanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This module is a configuration tool for managing what programs start up "
#| "with your personal &plasma;. It allows you to add programs or scripts so "
#| "they automatically start during the startup or shutdown of your &plasma; "
#| "session and to manage them."
msgid ""
"This module is a configuration tool for managing what programs start up with "
"your personal &plasma;. It allows you to add programs or scripts so they "
"automatically run during startup or shutdown of your &plasma; session and to "
"manage them."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj modul je postavna alatka za upravljanje programima koji se pokreću sa "
"Plasmom. U njemu možete dodavati i upravljati programima i skriptama koje će "
"se automatski pokretati pri pokretanju ili gašenju vaše plasma sesije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Please note that in this module all changes are immediately applied."
msgstr "Imajte u vidu da se izmene u ovom modulu trenutačno primenjuju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The program scans <filename>$HOME/.config/autostart/</filename>, "
#| "<filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-workspace/env</"
#| "filename> and <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-"
#| "workspace/shutdown</filename> folders to check what programs and scripts "
#| "are already there and displays them. It allows you to manage them easily."
msgid ""
"The program scans <filename>$HOME/.config/autostart/</filename> for "
"applications and login scripts, <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/"
"plasma-workspace/env</filename> for pre-startup scripts and <filename class="
"\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-workspace/shutdown</filename> for logout "
"scripts to check what programs and scripts are already there and displays "
"them. It allows you to manage them easily."
msgstr ""
"Modul skenira fascikle <filename>$HOME/.config/autostart/</filename>, "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-workspace/env</filename> "
"i <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-workspace/shutdown</"
"filename>, da bi pronašao i prikazao programe i skripte koji su već u njima. "
"Zatim vam omogućava da njima lako upravljate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Login scripts are <filename class=\"extension\">.desktop</filename> files "
"with a <literal>X-KDE-AutostartScript=true</literal> key. Pre-startup "
"scripts are run earlier and can be used to set environment variables."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you can change the location of your <filename class=\"directory"
"\">Autostart</filename> folder in <menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locations</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"<guilabel>Personalization</guilabel> category of the &systemsettings; and "
"set a different folder than <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/"
"autostart</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Lokaciju fascikle samopokretanja možete izmeniti preko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Programi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lokacije</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> u kategoriji <guilabel>Prilagođavanje</guilabel> u Sistemskim "
"postavkama, tj. postaviti je na nešto drugo umesto <filename class="
"\"directory\">$HOME/.config/autostart</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please read also <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmsmserver\">Desktop Session</"
"ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kded\">Background Services</ulink> "
"for information how to configure the startup behavior of your &plasma; "
"session."
msgstr ""
"Pročitajte još i o <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmsmserver\">sesijama "
"površi</ulink> i <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kded\">pozadinskim servisima</"
"ulink> za više detalja o podešavanju ponašanja pri pokretanju plasma sesije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some &kde; applications handle the autostart behavior on their own, &eg; you "
"can enable or disable autostart of an application in the settings dialog "
"(&kalarm;) or you have to use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (&konversation;, "
"&kopete;), otherwise the application is still running in the systemtray and "
"will be restarted on next login."
msgstr ""
"Neki KDE programi sami rukuju automatskim pokretanjem. Na primer, negde "
"možete uključiti i isključiti automatsko pokretanje kroz dijalog postavki "
"programa (<application>K‑alarm</application>), a negde morate upotrebiti "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fajl</guimenu><guimenuitem>Napusti</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> da program ne bi nastavio da radi u sistemskoj kaseti i da se ne "
"bi sam pokrenuo pri narednom prijavljivanju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Migration from &kde; Workspaces 4"
msgstr "Selidba sa radnog prostora KDE‑a 4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "To migrate your personal autostart setting from &kde; Workspaces 4:"
msgstr "Svoje postavke automatskog pokretanja iz KDE‑a 4 selite ovako:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy desktop files from <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.kde/Autostart</"
"filename> to <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/autostart</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte .desktop fajlove iz <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.kde/"
"Autostart</filename> u <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/"
"autostart</filename>."

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy pre startup script files from <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.kde/"
"Autostart</filename> to <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-"
"workspace/env</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte fajlove skripti pre pokretanja iz <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$HOME/.kde/Autostart</filename> u <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/."
"config/plasma-workspace/env</filename>."

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy shutdown script files from <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.kde/"
"Autostart</filename> to <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-"
"workspace/shutdown</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte fajlove skripti pri gašenju iz <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$HOME/.kde/Autostart</filename> u <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/."
"config/plasma-workspace/shutdown</filename>."

